channel.title: Titlebox on clients
channel.description: Well Im just asking the community to help me in a problem involving the titlebox image shown in 317,377, ect clients. Im using a 377 client but i realized that my titlebox image isnt loading from the picture that i directed it to. It just loads the old runescape titlebox which looks ugly to me. I went to class30sub2,sub1,sub1 and searched titlebox and changed it to load the titlebox image that i got but it still doesnt load. Anyone knows were does the client load this from? :p

item.description:
@fury_upon_u wrote:

if theirs a file in the folder that has the current pic on it, edit it using paint and when u open the picture u want, look for the location of the the client ur using and save it as the name that the default client pic came with and client the old picture and it will say this file already exsists to you want to replace and cick yes then compile. idk if this is wat u wanted but i tried.
